data.value: select "Products"."ID" as "رقم المنتج", "Products"."BarCode" as "الباركود", "Products"."Name" as "الإسم", "Products"."Quntity" as "الكمية", "Products"."Uses" as "مرات الإستخدام", "Products"."DayDate" as "تاريخ الإدخال", "Products"."PayDate" as "تاريخ الشراء", "Products"."ExperidDate" as "تاريخ الصلاحية", "Products"."PAYmoney" as "سعر البيع", "Products"."PURCHERmoney" as "سعر الشراء", "Products"."SUP_name" as "إسم المسوق", "SupCategories"."Name" as "نوع المنتج", "Products"."JoumlaRmoney" as "سعر الجملة", "Products"."Commation" as "العلاوة", "Products"."Discount" as "التخفيض", "Products"."Status" as "الحالة" from (("dbo"."Products" "Products" inner join "dbo"."SupCategories" "SupCategories" on "SupCategories"."ID" = "Products"."PRDtype"))
